All Implemented Interfaces:
gov.nasa.arc.mct.platform.spi.WindowManager
public class WindowManagerImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements gov.nasa.arc.mct.platform.spi.WindowManager

Implements a window manager. This is the platform default window manager. It is not designed to be subclassed by component developers. Uses a singleton pattern to provide only a single, shared instance.

Opens a component into a new window.

Parameters:
displayName - the display name for the new housing
nodeView - the node view role of the component we will open in the new housing
activeWindow - the current active window
horizontalScale - the desired horizontal scaling of the window
verticalScale - the desired vertical scaling of the window
component - the component to open in the window
